what_worked: Applied decorrelate, materialize_cte: Consolidated duplicate aggregations and subqueries into single-pass CTEs, computing both ascending and descending ranks in one pass over filtered item averages. Extracted the repeated scalar subquery into a materialized CTE.
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Materializing a CTE used multiple times prevents redundant re-computation
